跑得下, 凱旋而家係玩款，用左好多日本零件，感覺差左，對fork都係showa街車貨仔... 得吉利paul smart係o連屎fork<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ... 再高境界玩norton<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ... 哈利呢d笨重大牛完全唔係cafe racing.... SR改真係等你認識cafe款既入門之選，缺點係腳撻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ... 雙騎死撚左火真係煩.... 利申:我吹下水only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b86f2229ce7727c244c4fb1e194cf3a9ef57dc","tid":984430,"uid":98795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T18:01:08.000Z","msg":"香港班所謂cafe racer咪即係super 4 big one 改分離呔曱甴seat<br />\n再加一條過LED brake燈薄鋰電冬菇風隔<br />\n一係SR400 / CB400SS 換下裝飾件<br />\n10架有8架都係倒模一式一樣TRD (TaoBao Racing Development) 改裝 <br />\n無里性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acae0b45c8ccc597b1fb3f8d3df788c8b2f3896c","tid":984430,"uid":193016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f07aa4b0377afbe3b9b683093bca512612f6bf57","tid":984430,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14be3fdce86fdf046816d9fa45064bc317020e34","tid":984430,"uid":193016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:30:32.000Z","msg":"呢排睇ig見到，都一見鐘情，之後係咁google,發現要砌部正宗cafe racer真係好貴。。最折衷就已經係買SR400ss...<br />\n<br />\n利申：牌都未考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:06:32.000Z","msg":"Yamaha sr400<br />\nHonda cb400ss<br />\n2架唔同既野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋2架原裝都唔係cafe racer style<br />\n都係要改<br />\n當然你可以買人地二手改左果d<br />\n不過香港冇乜幾多部改得靚<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒<br />\n玩車冇得平<br />\n26已經相對平過46好多<br />\n幾皮野改車都嫌貴真係唔好玩好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/